<document id="16820654"><sentence text="Possible carbamazepine toxicity with terbinafine."><entity charOffset="9-22" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e0" text="carbamazepine" /><entity charOffset="37-48" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e1" text="terbinafine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s1.e1" /></sentence><sentence text="To report a case of carbamazepine and terbinafine interaction resulting in an elevated level of carbamazepine and associated symptoms of toxicity"><entity charOffset="20-33" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e0" text="carbamazepine" /><entity charOffset="38-49" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e1" text="terbinafine" /><entity charOffset="96-109" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e2" text="carbamazepine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s2.e2" /></sentence><sentence text="" /><sentence text="A 50-year-old Caucasian man developed an elevated carbamazapine level after starting terbinafine, which caused symptoms of toxicity with gait ataxia, dizziness and falls"><entity charOffset="50-63" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e0" text="carbamazapine" /><entity charOffset="85-96" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e1" text="terbinafine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s4.e1" /></sentence><sentence text="" /><sentence text="This is a first report of a drug-drug interaction between carbamazapine and terbinafine"><entity charOffset="58-71" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e0" text="carbamazapine" /><entity charOffset="76-87" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e1" text="terbinafine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s6.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" Although the mechanism for this interaction is not fully known, it is suspected that terbinafine decreased the metabolism of carbamazapine and led to increased levels that continued even days after the carbamazapine had been stopped"><entity charOffset="86-97" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e0" text="terbinafine" /><entity charOffset="126-139" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e1" text="carbamazapine" /><entity charOffset="203-216" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e2" text="carbamazapine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s7.e2" /></sentence><sentence text=" The Naranjo Scale suggests that this was a probable interaction (score 6)" /><sentence text="" /><sentence text="While several drug-drug interactions have been reported with carbamazapine, there are no previous reports of its interaction with terbinafine"><entity charOffset="61-74" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e0" text="carbamazapine" /><entity charOffset="130-141" id="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e1" text="terbinafine" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.16820654.s10.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" Prescribers should exercise caution when prescribing these medications together" /><sentence text="" /></document>